title: Integrated Chinese Level 2 Part 2 Textbook + Audio
description:
I scanned my book because I hate carrying the textbook around. I also know it's not on the internet anywhere (I tried so hard to find it earlier) so I think it would be helpful to some of you who also want an electronic version.

Enjoy!


name: Integrated Chinese (Cheng & Tsui) Level 2 Part 2 - Simplified and Traditional Character
file format: pdf, mp3
size: ~300 Mb

files:
ch1.pdf - ch10.pdf
misc pdfs
audio mp3 - both textbook and workbook (mod and original)

For anyone who wonders, the illustration is different from level 2 part 1 I don't know why. Audio also differs from part 1 (both the people who voice it and the quality). The original audio is so slow and lengthy (7 mins each) that I need to modify it to make it faster and more proper for higher level student. Original file is also included but it's not that good
